OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA bright end
OL,6,Fto the day with scattered showers,
OL,7,Fthese will die out in the east leading
OL,8,Fto a dry night with clear spells.
OL,9,FCloudy in west with further showers
OL,10,Fovernight.
OL,11,
OL,12,CWednesday:FIt will be another day of
OL,13,Fbright spells and showers, some
OL,14,Fperhaps heavy and thundery.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,17,FCloudy with rain or drizzle on
OL,18,FThursday. Bright spells and scattered
OL,19,Fshowers on Friday. Sunny spells and
OL,20,Fshowers Saturday morning, becoming
OL,21,Fdrier later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
